Description: A powerful, easy to use syntax for specifying and
        estimating complex Structural Equation Models. Models can be
        estimated using Partial Least Squares Path Modeling or
        Covariance-Based Structural Equation Modeling or covariance
        based Confirmatory Factor Analysis. Methods described in Ray,
        Danks, and Valdez (2021).
Imports: parallel, lavaan, glue, knitr, testthat, rmarkdown, DiagrammeR
        (>= 1.0.6), DiagrammeRsvg (>= 0.1), webp
